# Stock Portfolio Tracker

A simple Python-based Stock Portfolio Tracker that allows users to:

- Add multiple stock investments
- Calculate investment value for each stock
- Display a portfolio summary
- Calculate total investment value
- Save results to a text file

## Features

✅ Supports multiple stock entries

✅ Predefined stock prices

✅ Calculates individual investment values

✅ Displays a detailed investment summary

✅ Calculates total portfolio value

✅ Option to save results in a text file

